author: jwaldman
msg: change BaseStyle's implementation to use ConcurrentHashMap instead of ArrayMap.
Performance tests show ConcurrentHashMap is faster but uses more memory (3.3M for 2600 selectors) than ArrayMap.
It's easier to implement than a thread-safe ArrayMap, so the pros outweigh the con.
